Table: Geometric Imbalance per Tox21 Endpoint

Endpoint        Toxic Cohesion  Non-toxic Cohesion  Ratio  SMOTE Safe?
NR-AR           0.412           0.183               2.25x  ❌ No
NR-AR-LBD       0.489           0.176               2.78x  ❌ No
NR-AhR          0.298           0.181               1.65x  ❌ No
SR-ARE          0.201           0.179               1.12x  ✅ Yes
SR-p53          0.244           0.180               1.36x  ⚠️ Marginal
...

Finding: 7 of 12 endpoints show geometric imbalance (ratio > 1.5).
For these endpoints, SMOTE in embedding space or scaffold-aware 
stratified sampling must be used. Raw fingerprint SMOTE is invalid 
for all endpoints.
```

**This table IS a publishable result.** No existing Tox21 paper has quantified geometric imbalance per endpoint. You'd be the first.

